Magician's hiding place
One of the city magicians kept some of his property in a hiding place near the city. When unrest broke out in the provinces, the road to this hiding place became unsafe and the magician could not recover anything.
#subobj  1
Find the hiding place of the magician
The best thing about this place is not that it is difficult to find, but that people who are able to appreciate the value of the contents of a coffer very rarely come here!
#subobj  2
Search the hiding place
The contents of this hiding place would hardly be useful in snow ravines or dark woods, but may prove useful in a city.
